          "end": "static int flex_physical_justify_value("
        },
        {
          "file": "radiant/layout_flex.cpp",
          "start": "void align_items_main_axis(",
          "end": "void align_items_cross_axis("
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "vector_backend_api_adapters",
      "modules": ["radiant"],
      "reason": "CoreGraphics and ThorVG are mutually exclusive implementations of the same C API; these narrow wrappers necessarily repeat target projection and batch guards while dispatching to different backend state.",
      "regions": [
        {
          "file": "radiant/rdt_vector_tvg.cpp",
          "start": "void rdt_vector_set_tile_offset_y(",
          "end": "// Path construction"
        },
        {
          "file": "radiant/rdt_vector_cg.mm",
          "start": "void rdt_vector_set_tile_offset_y(",
          "end": "// Path construction"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "vector_backend_gradient_entry_points",
      "modules": ["radiant"],
      "reason": "The linear and radial gradient API wrappers share only required argument validation and backend acquisition; their common gradient setup is already extracted and their draw calls are backend-specific.",
      "regions": [
        {
          "file": "radiant/rdt_vector_tvg.cpp",
          "start": "void rdt_fill_linear_gradient(",
          "end": "void rdt_fill_radial_gradient("
        },
        {
          "file": "radiant/rdt_vector_cg.mm",
          "start": "void rdt_fill_linear_gradient(",
          "end": "void rdt_fill_radial_gradient("
        },
        {
          "file": "radiant/rdt_vector_cg.mm",
          "start": "void rdt_fill_radial_gradient(",
          "end": "// Clipping"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "vector_backend_picture_size_adapters",
      "modules": ["radiant"],
      "reason": "Picture size getters and setters are required backend-local API definitions over private RdtPicture layouts; promoting them would expose backend implementation structs.",
      "regions": [
        {
          "file": "radiant/rdt_vector_tvg.cpp",
          "start": "void rdt_picture_get_size(",
          "end": "// Internal helper: render a SVG_DOM picture"
